These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: indonesian, italian
There 2 different types of food: kiwi, lemon
1. the italian is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
2. the person eating lemon is on the right of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Nationality   | italian  | indonesian |
| Food       | kiwi | lemon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, water
2 different games are played: whist, poker
1. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
2. the person drinking water is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | water |
| Game      | poker     | whist  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, dannemann
There are 2 different nationalities: french, nigerian
1. the french is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
2. the french is on the left or right of the dannemann-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Cigar   | chaman | dannemann  |
| Nationality   | french | nigerian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, sprite
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daisy, amaryllis
1. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person drinking fanta is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |
| Beverage   | sprite | fanta   |
| Flower       | amaryllis | daisy |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-5::.
House: tower, ranch-style
There are 2 different nationalities: american, australian
1. the australian is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
2. the ranch-style house is on the left or right of the tower house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| House   | ranch-style    | tower    |
| Nationality   | american | australian |

