.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-8::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: singing, woodworking
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: november, april
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |
| Hobby   | woodworking | singing |
| Birthday     | november        | april |

