.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-10::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: comedy, musical
2 different games are played: billiard, whist
1. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
2. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |
| Movie-Genre   | musical   | comedy |
| Game     | billiard | whist    |

