.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-11::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: disaster, western
2 different pets are kept: ferret, turtle
1. the person watching western movies is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
2. the owner of the turtle is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2    |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster  | western |
| Pet   | ferret | turtle |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-12::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: orange, yellow
The people use 2 different means of transport: helicopter, jet-ski
1. the person who likes yellow is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |
| Color       | orange  | yellow |
| Transport   | helicopter | jet-ski |

