The people prefer 2 different types of sport: badminton, handball
1. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
2. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |
| Transport   | trike       | scooter    |
| Sport         | badminton | handball |

